Division algorithm
issue.body: I'm currently working out the details for the modulo operation, I thought about two different approaches. The inversion then multiplication and linear regression algorithm and the shift and substraction algorithm. I do not know which algorithm will work better so I am probably going to implement both and compare them.

issue.title: C struct
issue.body: Using a C_struct instead of a C++ Class for the field operation, since cuda does not support static functions in c++ classes, makes implementation of special operations easier
